 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乜都反，搞到自己好辛苦，又好浪費錢<br />\n部份香港人比大陸人更大陸"},{"pid":"7e854dc9b810289fc066d54dc4451d44ec826178","tid":935384,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:43:11.000Z","msg":"咪係! 唔准用高通! <br />\n<br />\n用自主研發CPU!"},{"pid":"f2408f7a3976c08190518b0ffe4af80837c91505","tid":935384,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2002年香港特區政府開始就《香港基本法》第二十三條，就叛國，顛覆，及分裂國土等罪行進行諮詢。<br />\n<br />\n時任保安局局長<span style=\"color: red;\">葉劉淑儀</span>專程到多間大學出席研討會，但研討會卻演變成雙方的一場舌戰，令研討會最終不歡而散。期間葉劉淑儀的言論引發不少爭議，當中最廣為國際傳媒報導者為「希特拉也是民選」。"},{"pid":"59a5b76b483113f0c8f1cd36db2d6de695a6a502","tid":935384,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:44:24.000Z","msg":"啱呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9d5f84569fc23c6695a72ecd176e8f511d7751","tid":935384,"uid":203983,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:46:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74ce32dd56e62354766c7a636f584421c8c1fb13","tid":935384,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:46:39.000Z","msg":"小丑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51232f3d894d195489a09936265964cadba637e","tid":935384,"uid":106634,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"fa9d5f84569fc23c6695a72ecd176e8f511d7751","tid":935384,"uid":203983,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"250e31d863704d36a810c1d242283b509034ef17","tid":935384,"uid":106634,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:37:36.000Z","msg":"唔好撚用an